== Large UFO ==
''2000-2100:''
A large UFO will fly around, looking for a section of your railway tracks to land on. It will land, and will be immovable until a military aircraft appears to destroy it. The aircraft also destroys an 8x8 patch of land around the UFO to be destroyed (this only affects town buildings, trees, and unoccupied railway tracks).

